277	vovimayhem	API Feature:  Inbound Material Logs	## What does this PR do?\r\n\r\n* Simplifies the `InflowOrder::BatchItem` interface through a new model `InboundMaterialLog`, which takes care of saving all the stupid, over-engineered stuff going on InflowOrder.\r\n* Implements a new REST Api endpoint for @walreyes\r\n\r\n## API Examples:\r\n\r\n### 1-a: Reading the list from the root:\r\n```\r\n curl --verbose \\\r\n  -X GET \\\r\n  -H 'Cookie: [OBVIATED]' \\\r\n  --compressed \\\r\n  'http://localhost:3000/api/inbound_material_logs.json'\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 1-b: Reading the list scoped by the inbound order):\r\nSame as `/api/inbound_material_logs.json?filter[inbound_order_id]=1`\r\n```\r\n curl --verbose \\\r\n  -X GET \\\r\n  -H 'Cookie: [OBVIATED]' \\\r\n  --compressed \\\r\n  'http://localhost:3000/api/inbound_orders/1/material_logs.json'\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 2: Creating a new inbound material log:\r\n```\r\ncurl --verbose \\\r\n  -X POST \\\r\n  -H 'Cookie: [OBVIATED]' \\\r\n  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \\\r\n  -d '{"order_id":1647,"rack_id":387,"product_id":3,"quantity": 23,"properties": {"mill": "Some Mill","seam": "Seamless","size": "1\\"","grade": "L-80","range": "Rg 2","length": "31.5","weight": "4.70","coating": "Bare","condition": "N/A","connection": "8rd EUE"}}' \\\r\n  --compressed \\\r\n  'http://localhost:3000/api/inbound_material_logs.json'\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 3: Retrieving a particular inbound material log:\r\n```\r\ncurl --verbose \\\r\n  -X GET \\\r\n  -H 'Cookie: [OBVIATED]' \\\r\n  --compressed \\\r\n  'http://localhost:3000/api/inbound_material_logs/69553.json'\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 4: Removing a particular inbound material log:\r\n```\r\ncurl --verbose \\\r\n  -X DELETE \\\r\n  -H 'Cookie: [OBVIATED]' \\\r\n  --compressed \\\r\n  'http://localhost:3000/api/inbound_material_logs/69553.json'\r\n```\r\n\r\n*NOTE*: The `update` action was disabled due to difficulties regading all the over-engineering... plus there is no use case currently for it.